Multicorn - Content Management Library
======================================

Multicorn offers tools to access, create and edit data stored in heterogeneous
storage engines, with a simple key/value interface.

Multicorn supports **multiple storage mechanisms** (databases, filesystems, and
more) with an **unified data access interface**, giving the possibility to use
**flexible and evolutive data models**;

Multicorn should run on most of the UNIX-like platforms (Linux, BSD, MacOSÂ X)
and Windows. It is free and open-source software, written in Python, released
under a 3-clause BSD license.

For further information, please visit the `Multicorn Website
<http://www.multicorn.org/>`_.
